{"tid":985464,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"（Netflix )有無人睇Penny Dreadful?","createTime":"2019-01-17T15:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T01:32:46.000Z","uid":45206,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2864bc3f1c5e6a57243173dcfdd2be3ba60e99","tid":985464,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"呢排講起Penny Dreadful呢套英劇 發現其實無咩人睇 <br />\n決定介紹幾個同事一齊睇呢套 <br />\n順便都同各連登仔介紹下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ssxmtxo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsxmtxo.png&h=706398c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YtMKriZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtMKriZ.png&h=460c3be8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事發生係百幾年前工業革命時期嘅舊倫敦<br />\n一名父親同一個神秘嘅女人為尋覓失縱嘅故人 不得不與魔鬼糾纏 交易<br />\n <br />\n當時科學抬頭 神學未衰 迷信與理性互相衝突<br />\ntime when science and superstition works hand in hand. <br />\n<br />\n而呢個只係佢嘅其中一個point.<br />\n當中重有好多哲學 文學 女性主義 性 宗教等等嘅討論<br />\n<br />\n而且對白非常詩化 寫得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先睹為快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我求其攞一段科學家Victor同冒險家Malcolm嘅對白畀大家望下<br />\n<br />\nVICTOR:<br />\nThere is only one worthy goal for scientific exploration: <br />\npiercing the tissue that separates life from death.<br />\nEverything else, from the deep bottom of the sea <br />\nto the top of the highest mountain on the farthest planet, is insignificant. <br />\nLife and death, Sir Malcolm. <br />\nThe flicker that separates one from the other, <br />\nfast as a bat's wing, <br />\nmore beautiful than any sonnet. That is my river. <br />\nThat is my mountain. <br />\nThere I will plant my flag.<br />\n<br />\nSIR MALCOLM:<br />\nDoctor, you have the soul of a poet.<br />\n<br />\nVICTOR:<br />\nAnd a bank account to match"},{"pid":"11709ac7dad336de3a703f599fd0a119d1581772","tid":985464,"uid":64159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"係幾好睇，如果鐘意陰暗野嘅話應該會好鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17119cd5a9c232c3a2414c8b933f80b557e5904c","tid":985464,"uid":67325,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"Eva Green好撚好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461b9aeae804c2617675d6601c3c2cbfa1ff1b27","tid":985464,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11709ac7dad336de3a703f599fd0a119d1581772","tid":985464,"uid":64159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"係幾好睇，如果鐘意陰暗野嘅話應該會好鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"終於有知音了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fe031af6f930e17f32b0c683398732cd5daa67","tid":985464,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17119cd5a9c232c3a2414c8b933f80b557e5904c","tid":985464,"uid":67325,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"Eva Green好撚好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"我係J Victor <br />\n佢講啲科學嘢 又講啲文學嘢嗰下好撚sexy<br />\n<br />\n利申絲"},{"pid":"fdaf3116e4e58dfe89813852023f882ff567908e","tid":985464,"uid":67325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201